[
    {
        "Key": 1,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "与薇蒂雅分别后，我们重新回到了学院楼群之中。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 2,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "依靠卡罗琳给出的坐标，我们很快便在一幢教学楼中找到了向下的密道。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 3,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "密道的入口安装着一个巨大而复杂的锁，似乎就是我们先前在庆典上听说过的，能够感应情绪的特殊电子锁。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 4,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "如今锁已经打开，而从入口处仓促而拙劣的伪装来看，埃达人间体显然已经先一步进入了里面。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 5,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "如今我们已经没有犹豫的时间，我朝着凯茜娅和苔丝点了点头，便先一步走进了密道中。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 6,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "通过了十米左右的楼梯和过渡区域后，我们的眼前豁然开朗。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 7,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这里虽然是深埋于地下的通道，内部的装潢上却十分华美。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 8,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我能看出，这条通道似乎经过了多次修缮，在一些墙壁上，隐约还能看出新近粉刷的痕迹。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 9,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "另外，密道的墙壁上每隔数米便布置着一幅画作，即使是我这样的外行人，也能看出这些画作十分精美。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "凯茜娅狂诗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc30ep6_girl015_01",
        "zh_CN": "这些画……似乎都是真品。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "凯茜娅在一幅画前停了下来，将其上下打量了一遍。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这幅油画上描绘着一名身着银甲的战士，在暴风雨肆虐的悬崖上对抗巨龙的画面，看起来冲击力十足。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "凯茜娅狂诗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc30ep6_girl015_02",
        "zh_CN": "我没记错的话，这幅画在十年前的拍卖会上被高价拍走，后来就再也没有面世过。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc30ep6_girl017_01",
        "zh_CN": "但它们现在就只是像普通的装饰画一样，被摆在这种地方。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 15,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc30ep6_girl017_02",
        "zh_CN": "啊，画的下面还有一行小字，“爱丽丝女士捐赠，2052年”。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 16,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc30ep6_girl017_03",
        "zh_CN": "那边的也是，这里的画都是不同的人捐赠的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 17,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc30ep6_girl017_04",
        "zh_CN": "奇怪，这些人为什么要把画放在这里呢？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 18,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我能想到两种解释。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 19,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "其一，她们认为，将画保存在这里，比保存在世界上的任何其他地方都要安全。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 20,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "其二是，这些画的确只是作为装饰，因为在通道尽头，保存着比这些画作都要珍贵的东西。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 21,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc30ep6_girl017_05",
        "zh_CN": "更珍贵的东西……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 22,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "听了我的话，苔丝与凯茜娅都陷入了思索之中。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 23,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "对我们来说，卫城学院的书库中保存着什么，完全是未知数，这件事对埃达来说也是如此。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 24,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "到底什么书籍才会让它如此魂牵梦萦，不惜花费这么大的代价也要得到呢？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 25,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我还是很难想象，在逻辑和理性的支持下进行行动的埃达，会因为一本书而做出这么多事情。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 26,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "除非，它有足够充分的证据证明，那本书很重要……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 27,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我的思绪忽然被一阵熟悉的味道打断。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 28,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……泰坦物质。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 29,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我伸出手，拦住了凯茜娅和苔丝。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 30,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "当心点，我们离埃达人间体已经很近了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 31,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "与此同时，我也在脑中呼唤起意识体埃达，但并没有收到任何回应。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 32,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "先前的预感变得愈发强烈——意识体埃达很可能遭遇了不测。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 33,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "先不要并排走了，我在最前，苔丝居中，凯茜娅殿后，互相保持3米距离。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 34,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "同声",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc30ep6_together_01",
        "zh_CN": "明白。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 35,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "狭长的密道中，只剩下我们三人快步前行的脚步声。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 36,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "散发泰坦物质的个体也在快速移动着，但我能感觉到，我们之间的距离正在渐渐缩短。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 37,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这时，我忽然再次停下了脚步。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 38,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "原因无它，在我们眼前，竟然出现了两条岔路。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 39,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "仅从外表来看，它们看起来并没有任何区别。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 40,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "而当我试图感受泰坦物质的气息时，两条道路的深处竟然出现了相同的味道。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 41,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc30ep6_girl017_07",
        "zh_CN": "通往书库的道路……应该只有一条吧？那另一条会是什么？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 42,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我摇了摇头。即便是我，也不可能猜得到这种事情。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 43,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "那么，要干脆凭运气进行二选一吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 44,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不，从理性上说，显然有更合适的决定。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 45,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "只要让我独自走其中一条岔路，凯茜娅和苔丝走另一条，这样一来，无论埃达人间体出现在哪一边都能有一战之力。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 46,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但这个选择实在太容易想到，以至于，我有一种即将一脚踏入陷阱之中的预感。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 47,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "凯茜娅狂诗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc30ep6_girl015_04",
        "zh_CN": "playername，左边的那条路就让给我吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 48,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不知什么时候，凯茜娅忽然走到了我的面前。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 49,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "凯茜娅狂诗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc30ep6_girl015_05",
        "zh_CN": "如果人间体出现在我那边，我有信心抓住她。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 50,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "凯茜娅狂诗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc30ep6_girl015_06",
        "zh_CN": "如果不在，我也能第一时间赶到另一边，与你们会合。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 51,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "凯茜娅狂诗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc30ep6_girl015_07",
        "zh_CN": "这是最可靠的做法，不是吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 52,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "正常情况下，我一定会同意你的想法。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 53,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但面对埃达，我觉得她并不会设下一个简单的运气游戏。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 54,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在这种时候分头行动，实在是太不保险。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 55,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc30ep6_girl017_08",
        "zh_CN": "分析员。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 56,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我看向苔丝，而她也走上前来，抓住了我的手。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 57,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc30ep6_girl017_09",
        "zh_CN": "没什么好犹豫的，让我单独走一条岔路吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 58,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "凯茜娅狂诗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc30ep6_girl015_08",
        "zh_CN": "喂，大魔术师，现在可不是逞强的时候。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 59,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "苔丝背过手，笑着摇了摇头。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 60,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc30ep6_girl017_10",
        "zh_CN": "凯茜娅小姐，我现在要行使作为胜利者的特权了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 61,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc30ep6_girl017_11",
        "zh_CN": "我要在今天独占分析员，而你，按照约定，你需要陪在他的身边，防止其他人偷跑才行。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 62,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc30ep6_girl017_12",
        "zh_CN": "现在，我要去为之后的约会做准备了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 63,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc30ep6_girl017_13",
        "zh_CN": "凯茜娅小姐，你要确保分析员的安全，把他毫发无损地留给我，好吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 64,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "凯茜娅狂诗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc30ep6_girl015_09",
        "zh_CN": "你……！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 65,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在苔丝突如其来的宣言面前，凯茜娅一时竟说不出反驳的话。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 66,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "而苔丝只是宽慰地笑了笑，便抬起头看向了我。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 67,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc30ep6_girl017_14",
        "zh_CN": "分析员也答应过我的，对吧？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 68,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc30ep6_girl017_15",
        "zh_CN": "在学校的时候你也说过，约定是很重要的东西。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 69,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她的眼中闪耀着坚定的光芒，足以让我相信，此时的她是做好了一切准备后，才宣布了自己的决定。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 70,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
